### List products (array JSON → list endpoint)
GET http://localhost:3002/api/products

### Insert via POST — persists in memory until file reloads.
POST http://localhost:3002/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Webcam", "price": 60, "category": "electronics", "stock": 12 }

### Read config (object JSON → record endpoint)
GET http://localhost:3002/api/config

### Patch one field (record endpoints support shallow merge)
PATCH http://localhost:3002/api/config
Content-Type: application/json

{ "max_upload_mb": 100 }
